The brand's locally optimized cameras stand out in terms of their photo-taking capability compared to other budget devices. This brings out a level of competitiveness with other smartphones brands. Currently, available information shows that the new phone comes with a 6000Mah non-stop play allowing for a longer-lasting entertainment experience. The phone also uses Hyper Engine technology which allows for the intelligent switch between LTE and WI-FI, reducing game lag effectively and making your online phone experience smarter and more seamless than ever. A cinematic display is also expected to offer an immersive experience with a 6.82-inch stunning dot drop display and 90.66% screen to body ratio. A slim display is also expected to allow for comfortable single-hand operation, ensuring you ease of use anytime.